    • fill

      public static int fill(Sheet sheet, ResultSet rs, boolean addTableHeader) throws SQLException
      Fill Sheet with data from ResultSet.

      The result set data will be appended at the bottom of the sheet.

      Parameters:
      sheet - the sheet to fill
      rs - the ResultSet
      addTableHeader - whether to generate a header row
      Returns:
      the number of rows read
      Throws:
      SQLException - if an error occurs while reading from the ResultSet.
